  "detailed_description": "MOMIBOSU is a precision 2D platformer with plenty of exploration elements<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/8c3d3bd655194dd02690d1314cc324f0.poster.avif?t=1747407848\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/8c3d3bd655194dd02690d1314cc324f0.webm?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/8c3d3bd655194dd02690d1314cc324f0.mp4?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay that makes you want to try again and again</h2>You've been beaten, but you'll do better next time. It makes you want to do it one more time!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/9f2503c0612c00d0975fa2068b5c6d90.poster.avif?t=1747407848\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/9f2503c0612c00d0975fa2068b5c6d90.webm?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/9f2503c0612c00d0975fa2068b5c6d90.mp4?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Abundant gimmicks</h2>Something might happen when you bump enemies against each other!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/1c102a77652c0be195453ddb0c8a8e42.poster.avif?t=1747407848\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/1c102a77652c0be195453ddb0c8a8e42.webm?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/1c102a77652c0be195453ddb0c8a8e42.mp4?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Try various things by bumping enemy characters against each other!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/0cc95d5071732726d0c91b4c7aa6ece9.poster.avif?t=1747407848\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/0cc95d5071732726d0c91b4c7aa6ece9.webm?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/0cc95d5071732726d0c91b4c7aa6ece9.mp4?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battling with powerful enemies</h2>Hone your technique to defeat fearsome boss characters!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/0d6c31a7ee37b1994ef8c41b64d24e1f.poster.avif?t=1747407848\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/0d6c31a7ee37b1994ef8c41b64d24e1f.webm?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/0d6c31a7ee37b1994ef8c41b64d24e1f.mp4?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Boss characters are not only human. There are also monsters!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/b24ea2cd2b0a0e5f66975ef51cae3b27.poster.avif?t=1747407848\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/b24ea2cd2b0a0e5f66975ef51cae3b27.webm?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/b24ea2cd2b0a0e5f66975ef51cae3b27.mp4?t=1747407848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Various enhancement items</h2>Powering up with items is important for fighting fearsome enemies!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/7c1a6314146a415dffd9df6dc0ad5f31.avif?t=1747407848\" width=462 height=248 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A vast map with plenty to explore</h2>Adventure from a small village in the depths of the earth to a new world!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/e5cd09a995514630b5ea32dad57d0d0d.avif?t=1747407848\" width=460 height=246 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure Story</h2>The story is like a road movie in which the main characters, a boy and a girl from a small underground village, suffer, rejoice and experience many things on their journey to a new land<br>Can the adventure that began in search of hope come to a wonderful end...?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487340/extras/36c58e026225a45075ad86cc39af29d2.avif?t=1747407848\" width=480 height=270 /></span>",
